OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining showers will fade away,
OL,7,Fleaving a largely dry evening with
OL,8,Flight winds. Cloud will increase from
OL,9,Fthe west later, bringing outbreaks of
OL,10,Frain before dawn. Winds freshening
OL,11,Flater.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMorning cloud and rain
OL,14,Fclearing north-eastwards. Turning
OL,15,Fbriefly drier but further heavy
OL,16,Fafternoon showers following, perhaps
OL,17,Fthundery. Drier again later. Strong
OL,18,Fwinds with a risk of coastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
