OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry but
OL,6,Fincreasingly cloudy and breezy on
OL,7,FSunday. Band of rain slowly
OL,8,Ftransferring east on Monday. Cooler
OL,9,Fand windy on Tuesday, with sunny
OL,10,Fspells and showers, occasionally heavy.
